wdi2-TX.VAL.MRCH.R3.ZS.def: Merchandise exports to low- and middle-income economies in Latin America and the Caribbean are the sum of merchandise exports from the reporting economy to low- and middle-income economies in the Latin America and the Caribbean region according to World Bank classification of economies. Data are as a percentage of total merchandise exports by the economy.
wdi2-TX.VAL.MRCH.R3.ZS.name: Merchandise exports to low- and middle-income economies in Latin America & the Caribbean
wdi2-TX.VAL.MRCH.R3.ZS.source: World Bank staff estimates based data from International Monetary Fund's Direction of Trade database.
